useEffect hook React ka ek built-in hook hai jo functional components mein side effects handle karne ke liye use hota hai. Yeh component ke lifecycle events ke sath kaam karta hai, jaise component mount, update, aur unmount. Aap useEffect ko kisi function mein side effects define karne ke liye use karte hain. 

