Graph data structure ek aisa data structure hai jo nodes (ya vertices) aur edges se milkar banta hai. Yeh complex relationships ko represent karne ke liye use hota hai, jaise social networks ya maps. Graph ko represent karne ke liye do tareeqe hain: Adjacency Matrix aur Adjacency List. Example ke liye, agar humein graph bananay ka code dekhna ho toh: 

```python
class Graph:
    def __init__(self):
        self.graph = {}

    def add_edge(self, u, v):
        if u not in self.graph:
