Design patterns programming mein reusable solutions hain jo common problems solve karte hain. Singleton pattern ka use aise cases mein hota hai jahan sirf ek instance create karna hota hai. Ye aise define hota hai: 

```python
class Singleton:
    _instance = None

    def __new__(cls):
        if cls._instance is None:
            cls._instance = super(Singleton, cls).__new__(cls)
        return cls._instance
``` 

