Python decorators functions hain jo kisi function ya method ko modify karte hain bina uski code ko change kiye. Ye aapko functionality ko extend karne ka tareeqa dete hain. Yeh ek function ko parameter ki tarah lete hain aur return karte hain ek naye function ko. Example ke liye, agar humein function ki execution time ko measure karna hai, to hum decorator ka istemal kar sakte hain. 

