Bubble sort ko optimize karne ka ek tareeqa ye hai ke agar kisi pass mein koi swap nahi hota, to iska matlab hai ke list already sorted hai. Isliye aap loop ko break kar sakte hain. 

Example: 
```
def optimized_bubble_sort(arr):
    n = len(arr)
    for i in range(n):
        swapped = False
        for j in range(0, n-i-1):
            if arr[j] > arr[j+1]:
                arr[j], arr[j+1] = arr[j+1], arr[j]
                swapped = True
        if not swapped:
            break
    return arr
```
Is se performance improve hoga jab list pehle se sorted ho ya mostly sorted ho.

