API rate limiting ek technique hai jo server par requests ki taadaad ko limit karti hai. Ye is liye zaroori hai ke agar koi user ya system bohot zyada requests bhejta hai, to wo server ko overload kar sakta hai. Rate limiting se aap server ko stable rakh sakte hain. Misal ke taur par, agar aap API ko har minute 100 requests tak limit karte hain, to agar koi user is limit se zyada requests bheje, to unhe error milega. Example:

```javascript
