Recursion ek programming technique hai jisme function apne aap ko call karta hai. Ye tab kaam karta hai jab aapko kisi problem ko choti problems mein todna hota hai. Yahan par ek example hai jis mein factorial calculate kiya gaya hai:

```python
def factorial(n):
    if n == 0:
        return 1
    else:
        return n * factorial(n - 1)

