Graph data structure nodes aur edges ka istemal karta hai. Nodes ko vertices bhi kaha jata hai aur edges unke darmiyan connections hotay hain. Graphs ko do categories mein divide kiya jata hai:

1. **Directed Graph (DiGraph)**: Is mein edges ko direction hota hai. Ek node se doosri node tak jaana hai, lekin doosri taraf nahi ja sakte.

   **Example**:
   ```python
   class Graph:
       def __init__(self):
           self.graph = {}

       def add_edge(self, u, v):
           if u not in self.graph:
               self.graph[u] = []
           self.graph[u].append(v)

   g = Graph()
   g.add_edge('A', 'B')  # A se B ka direction
   g.add_edge('A', 'C')  # A se C ka direction
   ```

2. **Undirected Graph**: Is mein edges ka koi direction nahi hota. A se B tak jaana ho ya B se A tak, dono possible hain.

   **Example**:
   ```python
   class Graph:
       def __init__(self):
           self.graph = {}

       def add_edge(self, u, v):
           if u not in self.graph:
               self.graph[u] = []
           if v not in self.graph:
               self.graph[v] = []
           self.graph[u].append(v)
           self.graph[v].append(u)  # Undirected connection

   g = Graph()
   g.add_edge('A', 'B')  # A aur B ke darmiyan edge hai.
   ```

Graphs ko search karne ke liye algorithms jaise BFS (Breadth-First Search) aur DFS (Depth-First Search) istemal kiye jate hain.

Data Structures ke interview main aksar yeh chizein puchi jati hain: Arrays, Linked Lists, Stacks, Queues, Trees, aur Graphs. Har ek data structure ki properties aur use cases ko samajhna bahut zaroori hai. Misal ke taur par, agar aapko Linked List ke baare mein batana hai, toh aap yeh keh sakte hain: 

```javascript
class Node {
    constructor(data) {
        this.data = data;
        this.next = null;
    }
}

class LinkedList {
    constructor() {
        this.head = null;
    }
    insert(data) {
        let newNode = new Node(data);
        if (!this.head) {
            this.head = newNode;
        } else {
            let current = this.head;
            while (current.next) {
                current = current.next;
            }
            current.next = newNode;
        }
    }
}
```
Yeh code ek simple Linked List banata hai jismein aap naye nodes insert kar sakte hain.

