GraphQL aur REST dono APIs hain lekin inke kaam karne ka tareeqa alag hai. REST mein aapko har resource ke liye alag endpoints banana padta hai. Jab aapko data chahiye hota hai, aapko multiple requests karni padti hain. GraphQL mein aap ek hi endpoint se sab kuch le sakte hain aur sirf wahi data define karte hain jo aapko chahiye. 

