Nginx ek open-source web server hai jo static content serve karne ke liye istamal hota hai aur ye reverse proxy bhi bana sakta hai. Reverse proxy ka matlab hai ke server jo client ke requests ko accept karta hai, lekin wo khud requests ko doosre servers tak forward karta hai. Isay set karne ke liye aapko Nginx ki configuration file edit karni hoti hai. 

