Password hashing ek technique hai jisse hum passwords ko securely store karte hain taake agar koi database breach ho jaye to passwords asan se nahi mil sakein. Bcrypt ek popular library hai jo password hashing ke liye use hoti hai.

Yeh ek example hai jis mein hum bcrypt ka istemal karte hain:

