Event-driven architecture (EDA) ek design pattern hai jisme applications events pe react karti hain. Ye architecture loosely coupled systems banata hai, jahan components ek dusre se directly nahi judte. Ek example ke tor par, agar aapko ek user action par response dena ho, to aap event emit karte hain aur dusra component us event ko listen karta hai. 

