Dono frameworks apne apne features aur functionalities ke saath aate hain, aap apne application ki zaroorat ke hisaab se inka chayan kar sakte hain.

HTTP methods, web applications mein data exchange karne ke liye istemal hotay hain. GET method ko server se data lene ke liye istemal karte hain. Misal ke taur par:

```javascript
fetch('https://api.example.com/data')
  .then(response => response.json())
  .then(data => console.log(data));
```

POST method ka istemal naye data bhejne ke liye hota hai. Jaise:

```javascript
fetch('https://api.example.com/data', {
