2. **Database**: Firebase ka real-time database tumhe data store karne ki facility deta hai. Tum data ko JSON format mein store kar sakte ho aur jab bhi data update hota hai, tumhe realtime updates milte hain. Yeh code dekho:

```javascript
import firebase from 'firebase/app';
import 'firebase/database';

// Reference to the database
const dbRef = firebase.database().ref('path/to/data');

// Data ko write karna
dbRef.set({
