Data Structures ke interview questions ke liye aapko kuch common topics par focus karna chahiye. Kuch common questions hain: 1. 'Array aur Linked List mein kya farq hai?' 2. 'Stack aur Queue ke use cases kya hain?' 3. 'Binary Tree ko traverse kaise karte hain?' 4. 'Hash Table kya hai aur iska use kahan hota hai?' In sawalon ke jawab samajhne ke liye aapko code examples dekhne chahiye. Jaise: Stack ko implement karne ke liye aap yeh code dekh sakte hain: 

```python
class Stack:
    def __init__(self):
        self.stack = []

    def push(self, item):
        self.stack.append(item)

