Big O notation ek mathematical notation hai jo kisi algorithm ke performance ya efficiency ko describe karta hai, khaas taur par time complexity aur space complexity ko. Yeh hame yeh batata hai ki kisi function ka growth behavior kaisa hai jab input size bada ho jata hai. Iska use karke hum algorithms ko compare kar sakte hain. 

Example: Agar ek algorithm ka time complexity O(n) hai toh iska matlab hai ke agar input n barh jayega toh time bhi n ke saath barhega. Aur agar O(n^2) hai toh time input size ke square ke saath barhega. Yeh samajhna zaroori hai kyunki aapko yeh pata chal jata hai ke kaunsa algorithm zyada efficient hai bade data sets ke liye.
```python
# Example of Big O
def linear_function(n):  # O(n)
    for i in range(n):
        print(i)

# Example of quadratic function
def quadratic_function(n):  # O(n^2)
    for i in range(n):
        for j in range(n):
            print(i, j)
```

React useEffect hook functional components mein side effects handle karne ke liye use hota hai. Yeh hook component ke render hone ke baad execute hota hai aur aapko lifecycle methods jese ke componentDidMount aur componentDidUpdate ki tarah kaam karne ki ijaazat deta hai. Iska syntax is tarah hota hai:

```javascript
import React, { useEffect } from 'react';

function ExampleComponent() {
  useEffect(() => {
    // Yeh code run hoga jab component mount hoga ya update hoga
    console.log('Component mounted or updated');

    return () => {
      // Yeh cleanup function hai jo unmount hone par chalega
      console.log('Component unmounted');
    };
  }, []); // Dependency array

  return <div>Hello, World!</div>;
}
```

Agar aap dependency array ko khaali rakhenge, to useEffect sirf component mount hone par chalega. Is tarah aap side effects manage kar sakte hain jaise API calls ya subscriptions.

Dependency injection ek design pattern hai jo humare classes ko loosely coupled banata hai. Iska matlab hai ke classes ko unke dependencies khud nahi create karna padta, balki wo unhe injection ke zariye lete hain. Isse testing aur maintenance asaan hoti hai. 

Example: 
```python
class Database:
