JWT (JSON Web Token) ek token hai jo authentication ke liye use hota hai. Jab user login karta hai, server user ko ek token generate karke deta hai. Yeh token phir har request ke sath bheja jata hai, jisse server verify karta hai ke user authenticated hai ya nahi. Ek simple example yeh hai:

