API pe rate limiting lagana bahut zaroori hai kyunki yeh aapki service ko overuse ya abuse se bachaata hai. Agar koi user ya application aapki API ko zyada requests bhejta hai, toh yeh server ko slow ya crash kar sakta hai. Rate limiting se aap ye ensure karte hain ke har user ko ek certain number of requests karne ki ijazat ho. Example ke liye, agar aap 100 requests per minute ki limit lagate hain, toh yeh kuch aise implement kiya ja sakta hai:

```javascript
