API rate limiting ka matlab hai ke aap kisi bhi API ko ek certain number of requests tak limit karte hain. Yeh is liye hota hai taake server overload na ho aur sab users ko services mil sake. Aap yeh kaise implement kar sakte hain? Yeh Python Flask mein kuch aise hota hai:

