Graph data structure nodes aur edges se mil kar banta hai. Har node ko vertex kehte hain aur edges in vertex ko connect karte hain. Graph ko implement karne ke liye aap adjacency list ya adjacency matrix ka istemal kar sakte hain. Yahan pe ek example adjacency list ka hai: 

