Queue data structure ek linear data structure hai jo FIFO (First In First Out) principle par kaam karta hai. Matlab jo item pehle aata hai, wahi pehle nikaala jaata hai. Isay hum enqueue aur dequeue operations ke zariye manage karte hain. Enqueue se hum item add karte hain aur dequeue se item remove karte hain. Yeh ek simple example hai Python mein:

```python
class Queue:
    def __init__(self):
        self.items = []

    def enqueue(self, item):
        self.items.append(item)

    def dequeue(self):
        if not self.is_empty():
            return self.items.pop(0)
        return None

    def is_empty(self):
        return len(self.items) == 0

    def size(self):
        return len(self.items)

queue = Queue()
queue.enqueue(1)
queue.enqueue(2)
print(queue.dequeue())  # Output: 1
```

