Binary search algorithm ek efficient tareeqa hai sorted array ya list mein kisi element ko dhoondne ka. Iska kaam ye hai ke array ko do hissoon mein divide karta hai aur search karta hai. 

Binary search ka code example:

```python
def binary_search(arr, x):
    left, right = 0, len(arr) - 1
    while left <= right:
        mid = left + (right - left) // 2
        if arr[mid] == x:
            return mid
        elif arr[mid] < x:
            left = mid + 1
        else:
            right = mid - 1
    return -1
```

Is function ko call karne par aapko array aur wo element dena hoga jo aap dhoond rahe hain. Agar element milta hai to index return hota hai, warna -1 milta hai.

Vue.js ek progressive framework hai jo user interfaces banane ke liye use hota hai. Isme components ka concept hota hai, jo ke reusability ko asaan banata hai. Components ek choti choti functionality ya UI parts hote hain. Reactivity ka matlab hai ke jab aap data ko change karte hain, toh UI automatically update ho jata hai. 

