Website mein search functionality add karne ke liye aapko ek input field aur kuch backend logic chahiye hoga. Aap JavaScript ya Python Flask/Django jaise frameworks use kar sakte hain. Ek simple example dekhein:

HTML: 
```html
<input type='text' id='search' placeholder='Search...'>
