Async/await JavaScript ka ek feature hai jo asynchronous code ko likhna asan banata hai. Iska faida yeh hai ke aapka code read karne mein asan hota hai aur promises ka use bhi hota hai. Chalo ek example dekhte hain:

```javascript
// Ek function jo delay karega
