Code coverage ek technique hai jisse hum yeh dekhte hain ke humara test suite kitni lines of code ya functions ko cover karta hai. Iska faida yeh hai ke yeh aapko batata hai ke aapke tests kitne effective hain aur kaha improvement ki zarurat hai. Aam tor par code coverage percentage mein report hoti hai.

