Input validation ka matlab hai ke jo bhi data aapke backend mein aata hai, usay check karein ke wo sahi hai ya nahi. Yeh aapko security aur data integrity ke liye zaroori hota hai. Aap isay kuch frameworks jaise Express.js (Node.js ke liye) ya Django (Python ke liye) mein asani se implement kar sakte hain. 

