```

Event-driven architecture ek design pattern hai jahan applications events ke around design hoti hain. Jab ek event trigger hota hai, to woh specific actions ya processes ko invoke karta hai. Isay implement karne ke liye aapko event emitters aur listeners ki zarurat hoti hai. Yahan ek simple Node.js example diya gaya hai:

