Microservices aur Monolith dono software architecture ke tareeqe hain. Monolith ek aisa architecture hai jahan poora application ek hi codebase mein hota hai. Iska matlab hai ki agar aapko kisi feature ko update karna hai, to aapko poora application rebuild aur redeploy karna padega. 

