Graph data structure ek aisi structure hai jisme nodes (vertices) aur edges hote hain. Nodes represent karte hain objects ko aur edges unke darmiyan relationships ko. Graph mein do tarah hote hain: Directed (jisme edges ka direction hota hai) aur Undirected (jisme edges ka direction nahi hota). Example ke liye, agar hum ek graph banate hain jisme cities aur unke darmiyan roads hain, toh har city ek node hai aur road ek edge hai. Python mein graph ko represent karne ka ek tareeqa yeh hai: 

