g.add_edge('A', 'B')
g.add_edge('A', 'C')
g.add_edge('B', 'D')
g.print_graph()  # Output: A -> B -> C
```

Snapshot testing React components ki testing ka aik tareeqa hai. Ye components ka output capture karta hai aur phir agle tests mein is output ko compare karta hai. Isse ye pata chalta hai ke component ke output mein koi unexpected changes to nahi aaye. Snapshot testing ke liye usually 'Jest' library ka istemal hota hai. 

