Is example mein, jab component pehli dafa render hota hai, 'Component mounted!' console mein print hota hai. Aur jab component unmount hota hai, tab 'Component unmounted!' print hota hai. `useEffect` ka doosra argument dependency array hai, jismein agar koi value pass hoti hai to effect sirf tab chalega jab wo value change hoti hai.

AWS (Amazon Web Services) cloud computing ke liye ek platform hai jo kayi services offer karta hai. Toh chaliye dekhte hain EC2, S3, aur Lambda ke baare mein:

1. **EC2 (Elastic Compute Cloud)**: Yeh service aapko virtual servers provide karti hai jise aap apne applications host kar sakte hain. Aap yahan servers ko customize kar sakte hain jaise CPU, RAM, aur storage ke liye.

   ```bash
