2. **S3 (Simple Storage Service)**: Yeh service aapko data store karne ki facility deti hai. Yahan aap photos, videos, aur backups rakh sakte hain. S3 buckets ki madad se aap apne data ko organize kar sakte hain.

   ```bash
   # S3 bucket create karne ke liye AWS CLI command
   aws s3 mb s3://my-bucket-name
   ```

3. **Lambda**: Yeh serverless computing service hai jahan aap code ko bina kisi server manage kiye run kar sakte hain. Aap function likhte hain aur Lambda khud isay scale aur run karta hai jab zaroorat ho.

   ```javascript
