Data structures ke interview questions mein aksar linked lists, trees, stacks, queues, aur hash tables ke baare mein poocha jata hai. Misal ke taur par, aap se ye poochha ja sakta hai ke linked list kya hai aur iski implementation kaise hoti hai. Example:

```javascript
class Node {
    constructor(data) {
        this.data = data;
        this.next = null;
    }
}

class LinkedList {
    constructor() {
        this.head = null;
    }

    insert(data) {
        let newNode = new Node(data);
        if (!this.head) {
            this.head = newNode;
        } else {
            let current = this.head;
            while (current.next) {
                current = current.next;
            }
            current.next = newNode;
        }
    }
}
```
Is code mein, humne linked list bana di hai jisme data insert karne ka tareeqa bhi dikhaya hai.

