   Example:
   ```javascript
   fetch('https://api.example.com/data', {
     method: 'POST',
     headers: {
       'Content-Type': 'application/json'
     },
     body: JSON.stringify({ name: 'Ali', age: 25 })
   });
   ```

3. **PUT**: Yeh method kisi existing data ko update karne ke liye hota hai. Jab aap kisi item ki details update karte hain.

   Example:
   ```javascript
   fetch('https://api.example.com/data/1', {
     method: 'PUT',
     headers: {
       'Content-Type': 'application/json'
     },
     body: JSON.stringify({ name: 'Ahmed', age: 30 })
   });
   ```

4. **DELETE**: Yeh method server se kisi data ko delete karne ke liye hota hai. Agar aap kisi item ko hata rahe hain to DELETE request use hoti hai.

   Example:
   ```javascript
   fetch('https://api.example.com/data/1', {
     method: 'DELETE'
   });
   ```

In methods ka istemal aapki API ke design par depend karta hai.

